name: VOLUNTEER TICKET - Brainchild Festival 2013
description:
Full weekend camping ticket for Brainchild Festival 2013 
Dates: Friday 5th July - Sunday 7th July

Volunteer tickets are £25, with a £25 deposit. 
Initially the price is the same as Early Bird tickets, but at the end of the weekend, volunteers will receive half of their ticket price back. 

There are a very limited number of these tickets available

name: EARLY BIRD - Brainchild Festival 2013 Ticket
description:
Full weekend camping ticket for Brainchild Festival 2013
Dates: Friday 5th July - Sunday 7th July

There are a limited number of Early Bird tickets available.
People wishing to volunteer at the festival are encouraged to purchase separate volunteer tickets.
